{
  "stem": "8072.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I says, I want to go out, and I want to get back to my, you know, to the work detail.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me a-- like with the finger her gave me a push and I fell over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the next day I went back and I says, I want to get out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, well, how are you gonna be working-- how can you work in your work detail?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I'll explain to him the-- who-- the company, I'm-- the work detail I am, and who that guy is-- my kapo and everything-- and he would probably-- you know, wouldn't have to work, do physical work and everything.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said-- so he discharged me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He let me get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that day, I remember there was like a hole in front of my eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like-- like when I walked, like-- like a ditch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I just-- it was weird.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I couldn't see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even so, that day, because in the daytime, you weren't supposed to be in camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were supposed to be out on the labor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had to hide out that day until the guys came back, you know, till the guys came back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I-- the next day I finally went back to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and that-- and that was in the-- you know, I went back to work and I got back on my feet a little bit over there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hid behind the barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I hid in the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I went in the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I don't know, if I saw somebody here, I went there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I saw them in the front of the barrack I went behind the barrack.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
